WEBVTT

00:07:27.261 --> 00:07:30.954
aliweza kuonwa na vyombo vya habari
na kufanya wamrudishie akaunti yake.

00:07:30.978 --> 00:07:33.666
Ila hicho ndio alichofanya--
kuonwa na vyombo vya habari

00:07:34.020 --> 00:07:35.529
Na waandishi wa habari hawaponi

00:07:35.553 --> 00:07:36.727
David Thomson,

00:07:36.751 --> 00:07:40.149
mtaalamu wa ugaidi na mtangazaji
wa Radio ya Kimataifa ya Ufaransa,

00:07:40.173 --> 00:07:43.736
ripoti zake zilifutwa kwenye
akaunti yake Facebook

00:07:43.760 --> 00:07:46.549
na akaunti yake ikazimwa
kwa siku chache,

00:07:46.573 --> 00:07:50.474
kwasababu zilikuwa na picha
zenye bendera za ISIS,

00:07:50.498 --> 00:07:52.554
ingawa alikuwa anaripoti kuhusu ISIS

00:07:52.578 --> 00:07:53.756
sio kuhamasisha.

00:07:54.253 --> 00:07:57.242
Na pia tuna hadithi kutoka kwa watu
kama mtu wa Misri,

00:07:57.266 --> 00:07:58.883
Ahmed Abdellahy,

00:07:58.907 --> 00:08:04.050
aliyeripoti hivi karibuni tukio
la Washington DC